title: Mass Production of Custom Injection-Molded Yo-yo's
description: Lead a team of 5 peers over a semester's time to manufacture injection & thermoforming molds for the production of 50+ custom designed buzz lightyear yo-yo's, featuring a custom press-fit between the two halves of the yo-yo.

title: Autonomous Robot Design Competition
description: Placing 6th out of 138 students, this autonomous robot was the culmination of a semester of design and fabriccation work, which was informaed by multiple custom-built MATLAB simulations to determine necssary hardware specifications.
